source.name: Health Service System2010 Health Plan Enrollment
source.description: This dataset displays the number of employees, retirees and eligible family members enrolled in Health Service System (HSS) medical, dental and vision plans as of July 1, 2010. The data encompasses the City & County of San Francisco, San Francisco Unified School District and the San Francisco Community College District. It is broken out in numerous ways - including employee versus retiree, by employer, and by plan. As of the date the data was captured there were 105,545 individuals covered under HSS administered health plans.
